视察，认为两人住的房间是同一层、房间正好面对面，病毒很大可能是经过空气传播，但相关证据还在调查当中。对于富豪机场酒店涉及新发现的新冠病毒变异毒株感染两个案例，相关防疫工作已开始进行。香港卫生署卫生防护中心已安排由11月11日至14日曾入住该酒店、与两感染者相连的三间房间12名人士到检疫中心，进行14天的强制检疫，暂时未再发现相关确诊个案。 针对最新报告的新冠病毒变异毒株，有专家指出，该变异毒株具较多突变，但暂时没有证据显示传播率高，没有在香港构成小区风险。香港两人感染“奥密克戎”，更多细节披露：一人从南非抵港，另一人住他对面"},"attached_info":"Cj4IvvOO1If3gNBKEAMaCDczODY2OTUyIIbDi40GMAI4ZEARcgk1MDIxMzUyMzd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"142 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-40166ef6416d62e39cb265a6614b7259_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"18_1638162518.4432592","card_id":"Q_500119995","target":{"id":500119995,"title":"步非烟为啥后来不写纯武侠的小说了？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/500119995","type":"question","created":1637314172,"answer_count":50,"follower_count":211,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[4017,241666,479898,480116],"comment_count":13,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8IvvOO1If3gNBKEAMaCDczNDE5MTcxIPzc3YwGMA040wFAEnIJNTAwMTE5OTk1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"131 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-7a3a8b89105aad34385ca4744b3acf30_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"19_1638162518.443993","card_id":"Q_500029056","target":{"id":500029056,"title":"中国动画为什么一直要不断尝试 3D 动画？2D 动画是否还不够优秀？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/500029056","type":"question","created":1637296924,"answer_count":41,"follower_count":125,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[128,1859,7929,13908,15840],"comment_count":9,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj4IvvOO1If3gNBKEAMaCDczMzk4OTcxIJzW3IwGMAk4fUATcgk1MDAwMjkwNTZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA